lead_paragraph: It might seem strange given Beauden Barrett's sensational form this season but the All Blacks' flyhalf could be the player under the most scrutiny in their Rugby Championship clash against Argentina on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Barrett Under Pressure Despite Superb Form
headline.main: Barrett Under Pressure Despite Superb Form
